      <title>日产股价连续第二天下跌，因投资者获利了结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/nissan-shares-slide-for-second-day-as-investors-take-profit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车公司股价下跌，两天内跌幅达 13%，原因是该公司与实力更强的同行本田汽车公司达成交易的消息推动股价上涨，投资者获利了结。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/nissan-shares-slide-for-second-day-as-investors-take-profit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 04:32:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金上涨 27%，在金属市场涨跌互现的一年中脱颖而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/gold-s-27-advance-stands-out-in-mixed-year-for-metals-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金价格有望实现本世纪最大的年度涨幅之一，受美国货币宽松政策、持续的地缘政治风险以及各国央行的购买浪潮推动，黄金价格已上涨 27%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/gold-s-27-advance-stands-out-in-mixed-year-for-metals-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 04:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>固定收益重获青睐，中国股票基金发行量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/china-s-stock-fund-issuance-drops-as-fixed-income-back-in-favor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着秋季股市涨势放缓以及债券再度受到青睐，中国投资者对以股票为主的共同基金的兴趣在 12 月份有所减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/china-s-stock-fund-issuance-drops-as-fixed-income-back-in-favor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 03:42:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国寻求对总统尹永哲发出逮捕令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-30/south-korea-seeks-arrest-warrant-for-president-yoon-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国调查人员已申请逮捕被弹劾的总统尹锡烈，此前他多次拒绝就戒严令接受质询。战略与国际研究中心高级研究员兼韩国主席 Ellen Kim 表示，她看到了一个“令人担忧的局面”，即反对派领导的国会试图弹劾尹锡烈的整个内阁。她在“彭博社：亚洲贸易”节目中与 Haidi Stroud-Watts 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-30/south-korea-seeks-arrest-warrant-for-president-yoon-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 03:12:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
